\v 21 Cˀoa⁴-ti⁴ jon² nca³sˀa⁴ cjai¹nca³ nta³ ji²tjo⁴xin²-lao⁴³, cˀoa⁴ co²ntran⁴ coan³-lao⁴³ cao⁴ cjoa⁴fa³ˀai³tsjen³-no³, nca³ cjoa⁴tsˀen⁴ qui³nˀiaon²³, to⁴nca³ ntˀai⁴-vi⁴ntai⁴ je³cˀoa⁴-sˀin² qui³si³cjao²nta³-no³.  
