\v 4 Cˀia⁴ nca³ Cristo, ti⁴je²-ni³ cjoa⁴vi³jna³chon³-no³, sa⁴sen¹jna³va³sen³, cˀoa⁴-ti⁴ jon²-ˀni³ si⁴ncha¹va³saon³ cao⁴ je² cao⁴ cjoa⁴je³ya³. 
\s1 Je² ni⁴ma⁴ xi³ jchi¹nca³ cˀoa⁴ je² ni⁴ma⁴ xi³ cho⁴tse⁴ 
